// Finds the OS-direct tracking entry for `ptr`, retrieves its size, swap-
// removes the entry from the array, and releases the pages to the OS. Exits
// with sentinel code 135 if `ptr` is not found (double-free / corruption).
function __slab_os_direct_free(ptr MachineWord)
