// Public free entry point. Recovers the owning mspan via __slab_arena_map_get
// (a lockless read of the immutable map). Routing:
//   * miss (span == 0): OS-direct pointer — free it under __slab_lock.
//   * same-P free (my raw id >= 0 AND == span.owning_p): lockless local push.
//   * cross-P free (different P, or a raw OS thread with no P): CAS-push onto
//     the OWNER P's remote-free queue.
