	// refcount header starts at 0 (alloc-at-0). With lowering no longer emitting
	// any incref, the binding/field store that takes ownership is the first +1,
	// supplied by the late SSA insert-refcounts pass. (See the header layout
	// comment above and the __mm_decref rc-guard.)
	__Internals.storeIndirect(slotBase + 24, value: 0)
